Dirk's gonna do it.

05:51.903 --> 05:54.133
-Dirk?
-Uh-huh.

05:54.906 --> 05:56.526
All rise.

06:00.411 --> 06:01.611
Please?

06:04.815 --> 06:10.145
Criminal court part two is now in session.
the Honorable Harold T. Stone presiding.

06:14.591 --> 06:15.991
You may be seated.

06:17.161 --> 06:18.891
Look what the cat done drug in.

06:19.061 --> 06:21.551
-Hello. Judge Stone.
-Christine. Christine Sullivan.

06:21.731 --> 06:23.131
