06:23.299 --> 06:25.789
-Don't tell me you've been assigned here?
-Yes.

06:25.968 --> 06:29.558
Well. feather my feet
and start me grinning.

06:29.739 --> 06:32.799
As usual. sir. you speak for all of us.

06:32.975 --> 06:34.435
-Remember Mac?
-Yes. of course.

06:34.610 --> 06:35.700
-How are you?
-Hi. Fine.

06:35.878 --> 06:37.368
Hey. that is a neat outfit.

06:37.547 --> 06:38.837
