-No.

06:39.014 --> 06:40.284
Well. it is now.

06:40.448 --> 06:41.468
[HARRY LAUGHS]

06:41.650 --> 06:44.810
You were here about a year ago.
weren't you? We had some problems.

06:44.986 --> 06:47.346
-Yes. we did. but we solved them.
-Yes. we did.

06:47.522 --> 06:51.932
You know. as I recall. I thought you were
ignoring me and not letting me finish my--

06:52.093 --> 06:55.223
-Mac. what's first?
-People v. Hoover, solicitation.

06:55.397 --> 06:56.457
--sentences.

06:56.631 --> 06:59.331
I'm worried about Bull.
He should've been here an hour ago.

06:59.501 --> 07:01.531
-Then why don't you give him a call?
-Right.

07:01.702 --> 07:02.932
Oh. hi. Judge Stone.

07:03.102 --> 07:05.432
-Hi. Roberta. How're you doing?
-Just swell.

07:05.605 --> 07:08.395
-Say. I love what you've done to your hair.
-Thanks.

07:08.575 --> 07:11.005
It's about time somebody noticed it.

07:11.177 --> 07:12.797
-Your Honor--
-Oh. that's all right.

07:12.979 --> 07:16.749
You haven't seen me in a while.
I wouldn't expect you to mention it.

07:17.150 --> 07:18.620
[SPEAKS IN FRENCH]

07:18.785 --> 07:20.305
Ain't it?

07:20.485 --> 07:22.575
Excuse me.
if I could proceed with my defense?

07:22.754 --> 07:25.284
Defense? She approached
an undercover officer and said:

07:25.457 --> 07:28.717
"Give me 100 bucks.
and I'll make your teeth sweat."

07:29.728 --> 07:32.388
-Sir. I realize--
-Roberta. are you guilty of soliciting?

07:32.564 --> 07:34.054
