-Yes.

07:34.233 --> 07:36.133
--answer that.

07:36.301 --> 07:38.031
All right, that's a $50 fine
and time served.

07:38.202 --> 07:39.262
IGAVEL BANGSI

07:39.437 --> 07:43.597
-Next case. Good seeing you. Roberta.
-You too. Your Honor.

07:44.008 --> 07:47.338
Um.... Your Honor. it happened again.

07:47.511 --> 07:50.281
-What happened again?
-You didn't even let me finish my...

07:50.448 --> 07:52.008
-Mac. is there any word?
-No. sir.

07:52.183 --> 07:53.913
-...defense.
-Kind of a rhythm thing.

07:54.084 --> 07:56.524
You'll be jumping into conversations
within the year.

07:56.686 --> 08:00.616
I even called Bull's landlord. sir.
He said Bull didn't come home last night.

08:00.790 --> 08:03.020
-Now I'm worried.
-Maybe he got lucky.

08:03.193 --> 08:04.753
Yeah. the circus is in town.

08:04.928 --> 08:06.218
[DAN LAUGHS]

08:06.395 --> 08:09.295
-Dan.
-There he is.

08:14.136 --> 08:15.656
Bull?

08:26.080 --> 08:27.880
He's splashed.

08:39.092 --> 08:41.653
Meet the gang.

08:47.435 --> 08:49.895
MAC: Come on.
DAN: Let's get him in here.

08:50.071 --> 08:52.511
Are they a great bunch of people
or what?

08:52.674 --> 08:55.674
-Yeah. Real troupers.
-Yeah.

08:55.843 --> 08:58.943
I think the bearded lady likes you.

08:59.380 --> 09:02.780
Lips that touch mustache wax
shall never touch mine.

09:02.950 --> 09:04.920
Put him on the sofa. guys.

09:05.085 --> 09:08.535
-Anything I can do to help. Your Honor?
-No. we can handle it from here.

09:08.722 --> 09:12.252
-He's lucky to have a friend like you.
-Yeah. thanks very much. Dirk.

09:12.426 --> 09:16.586
-May the Lord bless thee and keep thee.
-I appreciate it, Dirk.

09:16.763 --> 09:18.293
Are you all right?

09:18.464 --> 09:21.994
-Can I get you anything?
-Not a thing. thanks.

09:23.235 --> 09:26.025
Who the hell are you?

09:26.205 --> 09:30.505
I'm Christine Sullivan. We met last year.
I'm the new defense attorney.

09:33.279 --> 09:35.709
You smell nummy.

09:36.449 --> 09:39.889
-Bull. I'm ashamed of you.
-It was just an innocent sniff. Harry.

09:40.052 --> 09:44.112
-I'm talking about the drinking.
