Whoa.

10:23.995 --> 10:27.295
Come on. let's have a seat over here.
big fella.

10:27.565 --> 10:30.625
Good God. am I tall.

10:31.870 --> 10:34.810
-Who's Selma?
-Bailiff that used to work here.

10:34.973 --> 10:36.843
She died six months ago.
They were close.

10:37.008 --> 10:38.528
So after we rode the elephants...

10:38.709 --> 10:41.699
...we all climbed
into this teeny little fire engine.

10:41.879 --> 10:44.349
-Bull?
-Yo.

10:44.515 --> 10:46.915
I just heard about Selma. I'm really sorry.

10:49.553 --> 10:51.213
You're sorry?

10:51.387 --> 10:54.357
-How do you think I feel?
-HeY. listen. I didn't mean--

10:54.523 --> 10:56.823
It was my best friend that died.
not yours.

10:56.991 --> 10:59.581
HARRY: Bull.
-Yo.

11:00.927 --> 11:03.557
We all cared about Selma very much.

11:03.930 --> 11:07.990
But there comes a time where you gotta
stop grieving. and you go on living.

11:10.169 --> 11:12.499
What did you do to your hair?

11:13.639 --> 11:16.899
-Listen. Bu||--
-Why did Selma have to die. Harry?

11:17.076 --> 11:20.736
I mean. why couldn't it be
some sicko scum out there instead of her?

11:25.250 --> 11:30.020
I want some answers.
and I want them now!

11:32.690 --> 11:35.280
Oh. yeah. So we were in this bar.
see. and E|mo--

11:35.459 --> 11:40.489
-Elmo's the little guy in the ringmaster suit.
