11:54.376 --> 11:56.496
-Right.
-Mac. you try to juggle the docket.

11:56.679 --> 11:59.149
-This could take a little while.
MAC: All right.

11:59.315 --> 12:01.675
Dan. keep Bull here
and keep an eye on him.

12:01.851 --> 12:04.291
I don't want him roaming around
in this condition.

12:04.453 --> 12:05.893
[LAUGHING]

12:07.022 --> 12:09.922
So we took the ring of fire and--

12:11.227 --> 12:14.487
-I'll humor him till it hurts.
-I'll be right back.

12:14.663 --> 12:15.793
[DAN LAUGHS]

12:15.965 --> 12:17.625
Yeah. yeah.

12:18.733 --> 12:21.933
Anyway. I'm leaving.

12:22.103 --> 12:24.543
Oh. wait. no.
Bull. Harry said to stay here.

12:24.706 --> 12:25.826
Get out of my way. Dan.

12:26.007 --> 12:28.977
