Don't just stand there. Untie me.

13:22.861 --> 13:25.521
-What happened?
-Bull decided to go for a walk.

13:25.697 --> 13:30.067
I tried to stop him.
and. boom. twisted mister.

13:30.235 --> 13:31.285
Sir. I wa--

13:32.304 --> 13:34.434
Oh. my Lord.

13:34.806 --> 13:36.366
Dan. are you in pain?

13:37.641 --> 13:39.171
-No. not really.
MAC: Well, great.

13:39.342 --> 13:42.072
Then hold it right there
while I go get my camera.

13:42.245 --> 13:46.835
-Mac.
-Looks like one of those damn Picassos.

13:47.717 --> 13:49.237
All right. I'll pay for help.

13:49.818 --> 13:51.508
-What happened?
-Bull's on the loose.

13:51.687 --> 13:54.587
-Maybe we should search the building.
-No reason for that. sir.

13:54.756 --> 13:58.276
