14:01.695 --> 14:03.525
...roof.

14:03.697 --> 14:05.627
Not again.

14:06.399 --> 14:08.159
-I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
-It's all right.

14:08.335 --> 14:12.285
Nothing a few pins
and a few steel rods can't fix.

14:12.472 --> 14:15.102
Well. there he is. just like always.

14:15.275 --> 14:17.865
Yeah. So I wonder where he got the cape.

14:19.011 --> 14:20.341
Oh. no.

14:21.213 --> 14:23.343
-Mac. hold on to me. huh?
-I'm right here. sir.

14:23.515 --> 14:26.675
In fact. look. tie that. would you?
Just in case.

14:26.852 --> 14:30.482
-Uh-huh.
-Bull?

14:30.656 --> 14:33.316
Bull. talk to me.

14:33.492 --> 14:39.832
BULL:
The night has a thousand eyes.

14:41.600 --> 14:44.130
I'll send for some burgers.

14:44.903 --> 14:46.393
CHRISTINE:
Sir?

14:46.572 --> 14:49.302
